{"tid":2004668,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"小米Redmi Note9 國際版廣告才上架就惹一身腥，日本網友罵到上搜尋排行榜、緊急下架道歉","createTime":"2020-05-06T14:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T15:01:54.000Z","uid":104138,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"de74a8e90540d80286a9ddb5d9b87e0d790c479d","tid":2004668,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T14:48:42.000Z","msg":"雖然這則影片已經下架，不過有網友將影片備份了起來。從影片中可以看出，一名男子正在吃壽司，而這個壽司被做成電池的形狀，用來表示30W快充。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.techbang.com/system/images/555189/original/38a913d3f76d521ad740fb347a61be7e.jpg?1588762088\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F555189%2Foriginal%2F38a913d3f76d521ad740fb347a61be7e.jpg%3F1588762088&h=0521323c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n接下來這名男子將壽司吃下，表示接受快充。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.techbang.com/system/images/555190/original/61409cb945da1588f9814b6735224d78.jpg?1588762153\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F555190%2Foriginal%2F61409cb945da1588f9814b6735224d78.jpg%3F1588762153&h=79f0cc5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下來男子開始充氣，漂浮起來，變成一個「大胖子」氣球。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.techbang.com/system/images/555191/original/b35c70fa55096ae6b671042f134a91ce.jpg?1588762314\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F555191%2Foriginal%2Fb35c70fa55096ae6b671042f134a91ce.jpg%3F1588762314&h=8d0478bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男子飄到天際（日本長崎投放的原子彈名叫「fat man」），可以看出背景是日本的房子。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.techbang.com/system/images/555193/original/146491e00c6db98c1e28d48d4b64d345.jpg?1588762403\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F555193%2Foriginal%2F146491e00c6db98c1e28d48d4b64d345.jpg%3F1588762403&h=ecb05dab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n爆炸引出蘑菇雲，然後打出「快充」的字樣。<br />\n<br />\n整個影片很自然會讓人聯想到二次大戰日本被投下原子彈的歷史，也很讓人不解明明快充的表達方式有很多，為什麼小米偏偏要用到這些元素來製作廣告？日本網友可以說是一整個被惹毛了，紛紛上網批評。<br />\n<br />\n小米在Twitter上發表了道歉啟事，表示這隻針對國際市場的產品促銷廣告，在內容製作上有欠考慮，已經刪除該廣告。未來製作影片將會基於對世界各國文化的尊重，嚴防類似的狀況再發生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.techbang.com/posts/78328-xiaomi-ad-was-scolded-by-japanese-netizens-to-search-for-the-leaderboard-emergency-off-shelf-treatment?from=home_news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techbang.com%2Fposts%2F78328-xiaomi-ad-was-scolded-by-japanese-netizens-to-search-for-the-leaderboard-emergency-off-shelf-treatment%3Ffrom%3Dhome_news&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBf4N63GW6AE6v5vQ0jPanwo%3D&h=37ddfdea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.techbang.com/posts/78328-xiaomi-ad-was-scolded-by-japanese-netizens-to-search-for-the-leaderboard-emergency-off-shelf-treatment?from=home_news</a>"},{"pid":"c53641fe601df0430e3ff22ee2539495a192788d","tid":2004668,"uid":239489,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T14:49:48.000Z","msg":"[國際線聯署]<br />\n澳洲手足撐反送中比奶共UQ威脅開除<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2004038\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2004038</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"556c7987a785ef4325782c4cb44aeaa3d0988aed","tid":2004668,"uid":162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T15:01:54.000Z","msg":"度呢個idea 個條支那蝗一撚定覺得自己創意無限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}